def run(*arg): 
    import numpy as np
    import math
    sampling_rate = 8000
    fft_size = len(arg)

    xf = np.fft.rfft(arg)/fft_size
    xfpp = np.clip(np.abs(xf), 1e-20, 1e100)
    hxfpp = xfpp[: int(len(xfpp)/2)]

    max1 = hxfpp.max()
    max1index = hxfpp.argmax()
    masterHZ  = 0
    tonetmp   = 0
    tone      = 0

    masterHZ = max1index*(sampling_rate/fft_size)*2

    if masterHZ > 20 and masterHZ < 4000 and max1 > 3.9: 
        tonetmp = 69 + round(12*math.log2(masterHZ/440.0))
        tone = (tonetmp - 59 ) % 12
        return tone
    return 0
